         !text "As you near the front yard of the large,"
         !text "old victorian house, you feel an        "
         !text "unexplainable tension. A small voice    "
         !text "whispers inside your head, \"Open the    "
         !text "door and step inside, if you dare...\"   "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "Upon entering, the door closes and locks"
         !text "behind you. Inside the house lies murder"
         !text "and mystery -- it's up to you to solve  "
         !text "them. Who is the killer and what are    "
         !text "their motives? Where does the secret    "
         !text "passageway lead to? Who is dropping     "
         !text "those curious notes? And who will be the"
         !text "next victim... If you are not careful,  "
         !text "it could be you!                        "
